metadata.name: Pepemoana
metadata.description:
On the Polynesian island of Motunui People worship the goddess of nature, Te Fiti, who brought life to the ocean long ago. Using the stone of Ethereum as her heart and her source of power, the demi-god PepeMaui transforms the wind and sea. and the lord of the seas Stealing hearts to give mankind creative powers. However, Te Fiti disintegrates and PepeMaui is attacked offshore by the volcanic demon Te KƒÅ. He loses both his magic hook and his heart into the deep sea.
